him which to me meant you sit there she gets number 
two and sets him number three and she gets number

03:36.014 --> 03:59.018
four and she takes him behind these babies comes 
over here and she goes into this water and she

03:36.014 --> 03:59.018
catches um Red Horse Minnow. And she has it in both 
